Program: Discovery
Title: Water pollution in Lagos
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jry01
Last Broadcast Date: 08 January 2002
How Nigeria's growing population is placing a strain on its clean water supply. The infrastructure of the capital of Nigeria, Lagos, is under growing pressure as the megacity's population grows. Access to clean water is not widespread as the programme finds out. Picture: Water pollution, Credit: Getty Images Show less